trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: Representa un cuadro de diálogo que permite al usuario seleccionar un tipo.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase exige al usuario que explore una lista de Windows Workflow Foundation y los espacios de nombres de .NET Framework y sus tipos contenidos y seleccione un tipo único.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which the dialog obtains services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> del que el diálogo obtiene los servicios.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> del que obtener los servicios de filtrado de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: Nombre del tipo seleccionado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, and a string.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia nueva de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> utilizando <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> y una cadena.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> del que obtener los servicios.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> del que obtener los servicios de filtrado de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: Nombre del tipo seleccionado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> that allows access local assemblies to load in the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> que permite el acceso a los ensamblados locales para cargar en el diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, a string, and a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una instancia nueva de la clase <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> utilizando <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, una cadena y <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo seleccionado por el usuario en el cuadro de diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" /> seleccionado por el usuario en el cuadro de diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: Gets the component to associate with the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el componente para asociar al cuadro de diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> to bind to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> a enlazar con <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Si la propiedad devuelve un valor válido, algo que no sea una referencia nula, (`Nothing` en Visual Basic), el componente se agrega a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad es necesaria porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> devuelve siempre una referencia nula (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the container to associate with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el contenedor para asociar al diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> to associate with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> que debe asociarse a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> has not bound an <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Si <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> devuelve una referencia nula (`Nothing` en Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> no ha enlazado <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This method is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Se requiere este método porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> devuelve siempre una referencia nula (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el diálogo de explorador de tipos está en el modo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> is in design mode; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> se encuentra en modo de diseño; de lo contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad es necesaria porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> siempre devuelve `true`.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el nombre del componente asociado al diálogo de explorador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: The name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: El nombre del componente asociado al diálogo del explorador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propiedad es necesaria porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of service object to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: El objeto de servicio <see cref="T:System.Type" /> a recuperar.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Recupera el objeto de servicio para el tipo especificado.

trans-unit.source: A service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />, or a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto de servicio de tipo <paramref name="serviceType" /> o referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic) si no hay ningún objeto de servicio de tipo <paramref name="serviceType" />.

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: Si `serviceType` es del tipo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> devuelve un objeto de servicio.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: De lo contrario, devuelve una referencia nula (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).
